      <title>中国缓解打压担忧后，腾讯收复部分损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/tencent-netease-bounce-back-after-beijing-softens-gaming-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京方面软化了对有争议的新游戏限制的立场后，腾讯控股有限公司收复了上周的部分跌幅，这表明投资者仍对全球最大的移动领域再次受到打击保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-27/tencent-netease-bounce-back-after-beijing-softens-gaming-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 01:44:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
